names-israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-at-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018e-70fb-d1c9-af8f-7efbc8270000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨威胁要退出内塔尼亚胡战争政府，因为该法案草案豁免了极端正统派</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-dm-says-wont-support-netanyahus-draft-proposal-that-exempts-haredim/0000018e-706a-ddf4-a3de-78fa0d140000</link><description>以色列国防部长约阿夫·加兰特在周日启程前往华盛顿时也表示反对内塔尼亚胡总理起草的法案大纲，该法案大纲豁免极端正统派人士参军。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 14:35:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-dm-says-wont-support-netanyahus-draft-proposal-that-exempts-haredim/0000018e-706a-ddf4-a3de-78fa0d140000</guid></item><item><title>吐槽问题：以色列公司开发出第一个基于唾液的妊娠测试</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/spit-at-the-question-israeli-company-develops-first-saliva-based-pregnancy-test/0000018e-701a-d1c9-af8f-7ebbb5b30000</link><description>这种名为 Salistick 的家庭测试可以在月经推迟的第一天就检测出 β-hCG 激素，而月经推迟十天后，这是大多数家庭尿液检测的标准，并且 96准确率百分比</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 12:35:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/spit-at-the-question-israeli-company-develops-first-saliva-based-pregnancy-test/0000018e-701a-d1c9-af8f-7ebbb5b30000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人为什么要盛装庆祝普珥节？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/why-do-jews-dress-up-for-purim/0000017f-f77a-d044-adff-f7fb75f00000</link><description>借来的东西，借的东西？这一习俗似乎起源于 13 世纪的意大利，庆祝活动和化装舞会在忏悔星期二期间不断升级</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 12:27:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/why-do-jews-dress-up-for-purim/0000017f-f77a-d044-adff-f7fb75f00000</guid></item><item><title>“印度炸药”：在加沙，以色列国防军使用了 70 年前用于训练的弹药和炮弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-24/ty-article/a-huge-mess-in-gaza-idf-used-70-year-old-munitions-and-shells-intended-for-training/0000018e-5db4-d4b2-afcf-dfb626a90000</link><description>试图将弹药、非正规货物和“印度炸药”保存在分解的麻袋中，造成了后勤和行动上的噩梦，使炮兵部队难以协助作战部队，并增加了出错和错过目标的风险</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 12:22:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-24/ty-article/a-huge-mess-in-gaza-idf-used-70-year-old-munitions-and-shells-intended-for-training/0000018e-5db4-d4b2-afcf-dfb626a90000</guid></item><item><title>战争结束五个月后，约旦河西岸和加沙地带的居民为哈马斯的袭击辩护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/five-months-into-the-war-residents-of-both-the-west-bank-and-gaza-justify-hamas-attack/0000018e-65ac-da37-a3ff-77bc473e0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦民意调查显示，加沙人对袭击的支持率从三个月前的 57% 大幅上升至 71%</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 10:55:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/five-months-into-the-war-residents-of-both-the-west-bank-and-gaza-justify-hamas-attack/0000018e-65ac-da37-a3ff-77bc473e0000</guid></item><item><title>托马斯·弗里德曼：“内塔尼亚胡将作为犹太历史上最糟糕的领导人被铭记”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-24/ty-article-podcast/thomas-friedman-netanyahu-is-the-worst-leader-in-jewish-history/0000018e-6d2f-d8e8-a9de-7dbfc2760000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:58:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-24/ty-article-podcast/thomas-friedman-netanyahu-is-the-worst-leader-in-jewish-history/0000018e-6d2f-d8e8-a9de-7dbfc2760000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击导致以色列人权组织 B&amp;#39;Tselem 分裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/to-be-a-leftist-in-israel-after-october-7-the-case-of-human-rights-group-btselem/0000018e-6f9c-df85-afde-ffdd3fc10000</link><description>10 月 7 日的大屠杀在以色列人权组织 B&amp;#39;Tselem 中造成了裂痕。一名前高管对其提起的诉讼，让我们难得一睹以色列左翼人士在解释对以色列的袭击事件时的争论。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar